<h2 style="font-size: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.06em;"><span style="color: #1984ac;">What if God</span> took over your life?</h2>
<p class="unleashed_highlight">We are taking steps as a church to go beyond life as we have known it, to take new steps, and we invite you to join us as we are unleashed in OUR&nbsp;<strong>CHURCH</strong>, OUR&nbsp;<strong>CITY</strong>, and OUR&nbsp;<strong>WORLD</strong>!</p>
<p><strong>UNLEASHED</strong> is about a change of heart, a renewed sense of purpose and putting our faith into action. This is for everyone, including you. Whether you have been a believer for years or for a few precious hours, we have a pathway for you to grow in your faith and we hope that you will prayerfully consider joining with us in our story as Jesus empowers and uses us to change our CHURCH, CITY and WORLD for Him. This is one story that you want to be a part of.</p>
<h2>Ready, Set, Go!</h2>
